{"tid":836673,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"莊思敏沖涼任細妹𥄫","createTime":"2018-09-25T22:24:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T04:10:21.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9371275a37259949a071a9618106ce6f75348cd8","tid":836673,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T22:24:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/lmADyGPSRHRN2IzOH.uimw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/thesun.hk.com/5ef29c2e3dde2a0085bee5e1183800f7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FlmADyGPSRHRN2IzOH.uimw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F5ef29c2e3dde2a0085bee5e1183800f7&h=1e3538b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n藝人莊思敏和胞妹莊思明昨日出席護膚品牌活動，莊思敏透露早前到日本浸溫泉，不怕與人肉帛相見，她說：「冇所謂，我都會睇人，尤其同佢（思明）更加冇所謂，我哋喺屋企都係Share個洗手間，我沖涼時佢都照入嚟。」身材高挑的她，為免身高太出眾，受訪時刻意脫掉一隻高跟鞋，不介意單腳企。<br />\n<br />\n提到早前馮盈盈和莊思明對「公廁論」各有意見，前落選港姐工藤佑采突然在社交網發文暗寸思明，似有抽水之嫌，對此思明封嘴不提，莊思敏即講笑說：「好煩，不如你Delete個IG？」"},{"pid":"685d03fe2fa839f8daece57b570b4b8f9cd78773","tid":836673,"uid":45613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T01:00:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7095081a49d2164f67a102180ae09a274e92284","tid":836673,"uid":52339,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T02:34:23.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過最需要del ig既係莊思敏<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a673ed02af75e7a57a3fc9da2c80d2386ad2d69a","tid":836673,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T02:41:09.000Z","msg":"狗也不"},{"pid":"1a4defec9f6827b89c67ce94b3d0e6d97fd60c69","tid":836673,"uid":147146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T02:43:54.000Z","msg":"好撚樣衰<br />\n整得假波 點解唔整埋個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}